body:
#### PR description:

Remove legacy CUDA pixel local reconstruction:
  - remove the legacy CUDA beamspot modules and data formats;
  - remove the legacy CUDA pixel rechits modules and data formats;
  - remove the legacy CUDA pixel clustering modules and data formats;
  - remove the legacy CUDA pixel seeding modules;
  - remove the legacy CUDA pixel digi converter modules and data formats;
  - remove CUDA-related code from the legacy pixel converter and the `PixelCPEFast`;
  - convert the remaining uses to `pixelClustering` constants and `SiPixelHitStatus` data formats.

A separate PR will add back an alpaka version of the pixel clustering tests.

#### PR validation:

All unit and matrix tests pass.
